		<dc:subject scheme="SIheading">TRANSPORT</dc:subject>
		<dc:description>These Regulations implement in relation to the whole of the United Kingdom, Council Directive 2000/9/EC of 20th March 2000 relating to cableway installations designed to carry persons (OJ No L106 3.5.2000 p 21). The purpose of that Directive is to introduce common standards for the construction and putting into service of cableway installations, including safety components and subsystems incorporated into cableway installations.</dc:description>
