						<Title>SUBSYSTEMS OF AN INSTALLATION</Title>
						<P>
							<Text>For the purposes of this directive, an installation is divided up into infrastructure and the subsystems listed below, with exploitability and maintainability having to be taken into account in each case:</Text>
							<P1 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2004/129/schedule/1/paragraph/1/made" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2004/129/schedule/1/paragraph/1" id="schedule-1-paragraph-1">
								<Pnumber>1</Pnumber>
								<P1para>
									<Text>Cables and cable connections</Text>
								</P1para>
							</P1>
							<P1 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2004/129/schedule/1/paragraph/2/made" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2004/129/schedule/1/paragraph/2" id="schedule-1-paragraph-2">
								<Pnumber>2</Pnumber>
